{"tid":125766,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中行60萬歐元和解米蘭分行洗黑錢案","createTime":"2017-02-18T18:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T16:51:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ebebaf1611606d98a83cf4803d8023687cb330","tid":125766,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:11:45.000Z","msg":"中國銀行(03988)米蘭分行早前捲入洗黑錢案，據外電報道，中行同意支付60萬歐元(約逾490萬港元)罰款作為和解。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，於周五舉行的初步聆訊，中行同意支付60萬歐元罰金。法官同時裁定4個銀行職員洗黑錢罪名成立，判處緩刑兩年。<br />\n<br />\n中行稱，和解是為了避免冗長的官司，好讓米蘭分行可以集中精力拓展業務，又稱米蘭分行一直遵守國家和國際相關規定。<br />\n<br />\n─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─<br />\n東網已全面支援360影片及相片，讓你全方位睇盡新聞大事，恍如置身現場，立即登入東網360專頁：<a href=\"http://on.cc/360/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc%2F360%2F&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=b10deda9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://on.cc/360/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170218/photo/bkn-20170218172233606-0218_00842_001_01p.jpg?20170218181543\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170218172233606-0218_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20170218181543&h=e17df458&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"900fa49ee909c7afc87ff140cfd38f4667575af9","tid":125766,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T02:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1269324b37a1428775ac5e92a3a82895156fd81","tid":125766,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"曾志偉大法官：打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcd5224b7ecdec6e664f86227221a9cbe373944","tid":125766,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}